{
  "stem": "14737.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "To mingle among the students also-- so even the priest, who was by the name of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was a priest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was teaching religion there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was excused from religion because a different religion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the priest there also was talking about Christ.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think the priests also were not educated-- that's my opinion-- at a certain point, to a certain degree.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anti-Semitism was there, especially from the, from the teachers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Will I describe you in, in details?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, but this was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our principal in the school, he was the principal for the-- for both gymnasium, for the Russian gymnasium and for the Hungarian, was by the name [?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Dr. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Ropole, ?] a Czech, very intelligent person, who knows what democracy was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he probably kept it so that everybody should even-- he wouldn't let, some discrimination, all right.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But you couldn't prevent those teachers in, inside the class not being a little bit hostile, making remarks about Jews, not about person like myself, but about Jews.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so the children or the-- the-- who went there, the students, from-- who were the students also from different places, not from Beregsaz, who are like the children from teachers, from priests.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They [INAUDIBLE] also together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were not anti-Semite, because they didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was-- [? and I were-- ?] time, at that time, an anti-Semite wasn't to be understood like today.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't politically so much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe the Jew is better off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had the store, so you saw the Jew better off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he-- the non-Jew was maybe anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why is he better off?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But most-- Did you have friends among the non-Jews in this gymnasium?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had-- yeah, I had friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
